headline: Prophetic to Power D.R. Horton's AI-Driven Land Acquisition at National Scale
summary: Prophetic, an AI-native platform for land acquisition and development analysis, today announced that D.R. Horton, the largest U.S. homebuilder, has selected its platform for an org-wide deployment across 30+ states.
